org.multigraph
Interface Data.ReadyHandler

Enclosing class:
Data
public static interface Data.ReadyHandler

Objects adhering to the Data.ReadyHandler interface can be registered with a Data object via its onReady() method; the registered object's dataReady() method will be called whenever new data is available in the Data object.
